t to be for my partner and I.  The event was posted well in advance (late October in fact) on stratics or somewhere, so to the rest of you who put posts here after that complaining about no events, it may do you well to read the news before posting your gripes.  There were announcements at this last event of another event coming up in Greater Faydark next Friday night (11/19), so there's your chance if you missed out on the last one!</FONT></TD></TR><TR bgcolor="#D9DCE8"><TD valign=top><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana">Mithandriel</FONT></TD><TD><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana">Just some shameless advertising:<P>The Brotherhood Frost will be hosting "Adopt a Zone" this Sunday evening (around 7PM(EST) in North Ro.  We will be providing healing, buffing, curing, etc at the major points of interest (derv camps, platform, etc) as well as have some newbie and low level give aways and contests. Some items that will be given away/contest prizes will be banded, bronze, pathcwork and raw-hide armor, FS weapons, black iron medallions, spiked and studded leather collars and many other things.<P>This will mainly be for players around 15th and under (non-twinked).  The event will be announced in the zone as it will be starting.  <P>I hope to you see you all there.<P>Mithandriel Fireforge<BR>29th level servant of Brell Siriliis<BR>Brotherhood Frost</FONT></TD></TR></TABLE></td></tr></table> 
